Insider Activity


Individual




William P. Stiritz



Mr. William P. Stiritz is Non-Executive Chairman at Post Holdings, Inc. He is on the Board of Directors at Aldabra 3 Acquisition Corp.
Mr. Stiritz was previously employed as a Director-Emeritus by Reliance Bancshares, Inc., Chairman-Emeritus by Energizer Holdings, Inc., Chairman, President & Chief Executive Officer by Agribrands International, Inc., Chairman by Ralcorp Holdings, Inc., Chief Executive Officer by Ralston Purina Co., and Partner by Westgate Group LLC. He also served on the board at Macy's, Inc., Vail Resorts, Inc., Ball Corp., and The May Department Stores Co.
He received his undergraduate degree from Northwestern University and a graduate degree from St. Louis University.



